title: Maharani India Restaurant
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A typical meal is represented by a thali , a large stainless steel plate with small bowel dishes containing rice, naan, or puri, or roti or paratha (flat breads), dhal (lentil), vegetables or meat (non-vegetarian), chutney or pickle and yogurt. Appetizers are separated as to vegetarian and non-vegetarian (modifiable), and the 20+ vegetable dishes can be modified (i.e. "exclude cheese") to stay vegan.
